WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:01.839
Section

00:00:01.839 --> 00:00:04.240
one of doña Perfecta.

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:06.799
This is a Libbry Box Recording,

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:10.320
all Libbry Box Recordings aring the public domain.

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:13.040
For more information on to volunteer,

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:15.679
